    {
        "content": "<p>(I find <code>mod_cases</code> to be a little awkward because it puts <code>n % 6 = 1</code> into the form <code>Int.ModEq 6 n 1</code> for example, pretty printed as <code>n ≡ 1 [ZMOD 6]</code>)</p>",
